    "explanation": "<p>In the given figure, the number associated with the rectangle triangle and ellipse are 1,2 and 1 respectively.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/fly/@width/image/jaoe38c1mdiej628/bdf37604-d831-48e4-939a-02fdbcac3629/28140700-691b-11f0-ae9a-65ebc10bb442/file-jaoe38c1mdiej629.png?format=png\" data-orsrc=\"https://app-content.cdn.examgoal.net/image/jaoe38c1mdiej628/bdf37604-d831-48e4-939a-02fdbcac3629/28140700-691b-11f0-ae9a-65ebc10bb442/file-jaoe38c1mdiej629.png\" loading=\"lazy\" style=\"max-width:100%;height:auto;display:block;margin:0 auto;max-height:40vh;vertical-align:baseline\" alt=\"GATE AI 2025 General Aptitude - Logical Reasoning Question 4 English Explanation\"></p>\n<p>From figure :</p>\n<p>(i) $\\quad \\mathrm{P}$ (Inside the ellipse and rectangle)</p>\n\n<p></p><p>The number associated with the rectangle is 1 .</p><p></p>\n<p></p><p>The number associated with the ellipse is 3 .</p><p></p>\n<p></p><p>The sum of these two numbers.</p><p></p>\n\n<p>$$ P=1+3=4 $$</p>\n<p>(ii) $\\quad \\mathrm{Q}$ (Inside the ellipse and triangle)</p>\n\n<p></p><p>The number of associated with the ellipse is 3 .</p><p></p>\n<p></p><p>The number associated with the triangle is 2 .</p><p></p>\n<p></p><p>The sum of these two numbers</p><p></p>\n\n<p>$$ Q=3+2=5 $$</p>\n<p>(iii) $\\quad \\mathrm{R}$ (Inside all three shapes)</p>\n\n<p></p><p>The number associated with the rectangle is 1 .</p><p></p>\n<p></p><p>The number associated with the triangle is 2 .</p><p></p>\n<p></p><p>The number associated with the ellipse is 3 .</p><p></p>\n<p></p><p>The sum of these three numbers</p><p></p>\n\n<p>$$ R=1+2+3=6 $$</p>\n<p>Hence, the correct option is (B).</p>",
